      • getSynch

        public java.lang.String getSynch()
        Get the action label for this command. For independent ("tau"-labelled) commands, this is the empty string "" (it should never be null).

      • getSynchIndex

        public int getSynchIndex()
        Get the index of the action label for this command (in the model's list of actions). This is 1-indexed, with 0 denoting an independent ("tau"-labelled) command. // -1 denotes not (yet) known.
